lead_paragraph: Overnight leader Peter Uihlein of the United States shot a 4-under 68 and was tied for the second-round lead with Brett Rumford at the Perth International, with former British Open champion Louis Oosthuizen a stroke behind on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Uihlein, Rumford Share 2nd-Round Lead at Perth International
